<scope ilk="blob" lang="PHP" name="FileCommentSniff.php" src="/usr/local/pear/share/pear/PHP/CodeSniffer/Standards/PEAR/Sniffs/Commenting/FileCommentSniff.php"><scope doc="Parses and verifies the doc comments for files.&#10;&#10;Verifies that :&#10;&lt;ul&gt;&#10; &lt;li&gt;A doc comment exists.&lt;/li&gt;&#10; &lt;li&gt;There is a blank newline after the short description.&lt;/li&gt;&#10; &lt;li&gt;There is a blank newline between the long and short description.&lt;/li&gt;&#10; &lt;li&gt;There is a blank newline between the long description and tags.&lt;/li&gt;&#10; &lt;li&gt;A PHP version is specified.&lt;/li&gt;&#10; &lt;li&gt;Check the order of the tags.&lt;/li&gt;&#10; &lt;li&gt;Check the indentation of each tag.&lt;/li&gt;&#10; &lt;li&gt;Check required and optional tags and the format of their content.&lt;/li&gt;&#10;&lt;/ul&gt;&#10;&#10;@category  PHP&#10;@package   PHP_CodeSniffer&#10;@author    Greg Sherwood &lt;gsherwood@squiz.net&gt;&#10;@author    Marc McIntyre &lt;mmcintyre@squiz.net&gt;&#10;@copyright 2006-2012 Squiz Pty Ltd (ABN 77 084 670 600)&#10;@license   https://github.com/squizlabs/PHP_CodeSniffer/blob/master/licence.txt BSD Licence&#10;@version   Release: 1.4.6&#10;@link      http://pear.php.net/package/PHP_CodeSniffer" ilk="class" interfacerefs="PHP_CodeSniffer_Sniff" line="45" lineend="789" name="PEAR_Sniffs_Commenting_FileCommentSniff"><variable attributes="protected" citdl="PHP_CodeSniffer_Comment_Parser_ClassCommentParser" doc="The header comment parser for the current file.&#10;&#10;@var PHP_CodeSniffer_Comment_Parser_ClassCommentParser" line="53" name="commentParser" /><variable attributes="protected" citdl="PHP_CodeSniffer_File" doc="The current PHP_CodeSniffer_File object we are processing.&#10;&#10;@var PHP_CodeSniffer_File" line="60" name="currentFile" /><variable attributes="protected" citdl="array" doc="Tags in correct order and related info.&#10;&#10;@var array" line="123" name="tags" /><scope attributes="public" doc="Returns an a